        <p>Navigate to the snippet that you want to insert and select it. By using the buttons in the local toolbar, you can view all snippet files in a list, view files in their folder structure, and use other options. If you want to add one of your 20 most recently used snippets to the project, you can select a snippet from the Recently Used Snippets group. If you want to add one of your pinned—or favorite—snippets to the project, you can select a snippet from the Pinned Snippets group. You also can click <img src="../../Images/browse_ellipses.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareNotPrintedManual" /> to find and select a snippet file outside of the project.</p>
